des: This is a fan made skill for Amazon's Echo. Once installed, you will be able to ask Alexa for an unofficial random Arnold quote. These famous quotes are from previous movies and may even insult you! Not affiliated or officially sponsored by Arnold.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
